### User

# 1Ô∏è‚É£ Register
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/API/auth/register \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name":"Omar","email":"umara.loves@gmail.com","password":"123456"}'
```

# 2Ô∏è‚É£ Login
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/API/auth/login \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"email":"umara.loves@gmail.com","password":"NewPassword123"}'
```

# 3Ô∏è‚É£ Get Profile (Requires JWT)
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:5000/API/auth/me \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>"
```

# 4Ô∏è‚É£ Update Profile
```bash
curl -X PUT http://localhost:5000/API/auth/me/update \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <token>" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name":"Omar Ali","city":"Kolkata"}'
```


# 5Ô∏è‚É£ Forgot Password
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/API/auth/password/forgot \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"email":"umara.loves@gmail.com"}'
```


# 5Ô∏è‚É£ Reset Password
```bash
curl -X PUT http://localhost:5000/API/auth/password/reset/<Token> \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
        "password": "NewPassword123",
        "confirmPassword": "NewPassword123"
      }'
```

### Logout
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:5000/API/auth/logout 
```


### Product

# Add Product With Admin
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/API/products \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY4Zjk0ZGU0NTBiMjg2YjNjNDM3ZjhkNSIsInJvbGUiOiJ1c2VyIiwiaWF0IjoxNzYxMTc5NTEyLCJleHAiOjE3NjE3ODQzMTJ9.2zQvxbQhBCDDOp1_zMN8ZAzMqkPyXD3iKpGx7i45-hs" \
  -d '{
        "name": "Diamond Necklace",
        "description": "18k gold diamond necklace with elegant design",
        "price": 1299.99,
        "category": "Necklace",
        "brand": "DIVA",
        "material": "Gold",
        "stock": 10,
        "images": [
          { "url": "necklace1.jpg" },
          { "url": "necklace2.jpg" }
        ],
        "isFeatured": true,
        "tags": ["diamond", "luxury", "necklace"]
      }'
```

# Get all products (Public)
```bash
curl -X GET "http://localhost:5000/API/products?keyword=gold&sort=price&order=asc&page=1&limit=10"
```

+ You can use filters:
?keyword=gold
?category=Ring
?price[lte]=2000
?price[gte]=500

# Get a single product (by ID or slug)
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:5000/API/products/6718895c8b4f7d221c72b4f1
```
or by slug (if your model supports it):

```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:5000/API/products/diamond-necklace
```

# Update a product (Admin only)
```bash
curl -X PUT http://localhost:5000/API/products/<id> \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <your_admin_token>" \
  -d '{
        "price": 1499.99,
        "stock": 8,
        "isFeatured": false
      }'
```

# Delete a product (Admin only)
```bash
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:5000/API/products/6718895c8b4f7d221c72b4f1 \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <your_admin_token>"
```

# Add a product review (Authenticated User)
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/products/6718895c8b4f7d221c72b4f1/review \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer <user_token>" \
  -d '{
        "rating": 5,
        "comment": "Absolutely stunning piece! Worth every penny."
      }'
```

# üè∑Ô∏è Get featured products (Public)
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:5000/API/products/collections/featured
```

# üÜï Get new arrivals (Public)
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:5000/API/products/collections/new
```

# üíé Get best sellers (Public)
```bash
curl -X GET http://localhost:5000/API/products/collections/best
```
